íŸ@070dbb81c4a224a3e90faab2d3b66d6d6ef9fb211c23356b5fe27bc543aa7fa6ŸÛTitle: title: source-env
Path: Examples
Content:
Sources the environment from foo.nu in the current context.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> source-env foo.nu


```
Sourcing 
``null``
 is a no-op.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> source-env null


```
